OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FA bus driver has admitted killing two
OL,7,Fwomen after he hit the accelerator
OL,8,Finstead of brakes and his double-
OL,9,Fdecker ploughed into a bus stop.
OL,11,FBaruania Baros, 35, had been trying to
OL,12,Fmanoeuvre his vehicle to deploy a ramp
OL,13,Fto let a disabled passenger off his
OL,14,Fbus at the busy Piccadilly bus station
OL,15,Fin central Manchester around 9.25pm on
OL,16,FJuly 10 2022.
