OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FBut in an "unfortunate lapse of
OL,7,Fconcentration" he left the vehicle in
OL,8,Fgear causing it to lurch forward
OL,9,Fbefore mistakenly pressing the
OL,10,Faccelerator instead of the brake,
OL,11,FManchester Magistrates' Court heard.
OL,13,FThe bus mounted the pavement and
OL,14,Fploughed into the bus shelter where
OL,15,FJoyce Bacon, 60 and Adele Boylin, 55,
OL,16,Fwere standing.
