OL,6,FMrs Bacon, described by her family as
OL,7,Fa "loving mother, sister and wife" had
OL,8,Fbeen waiting with her husband, Ian,
OL,9,Fafter an evening out to the cinema,
OL,10,Fand mother-of-four Ms Boylin had
OL,11,Ffinished her shift in admin at
OL,12,FManchester Eye Hospital and was on her
OL,13,Fway home from work.
OL,15,FThe two women, who knew each other and
OL,16,Fwere stood together, were severely
OL,17,Finjured, Mrs Bacon killed at the scene
OL,18,Fand Ms Boylin dying six months later
OL,19,Fin hospital due to her injuries.
