OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FBaros, of Bentinck Street, Ashton-
OL,7,FUnder-Lyne, Greater Manchester, on
OL,8,FThursday admitted two counts of
OL,9,Fcausing death by careless driving.
OL,11,FHead bowed, he was disqualified from
OL,12,Fdriving immediately after entering his
OL,13,Fguilty pleas.
OL,15,FJP Monica Sim told him the 12-month
OL,16,Fmaximum jail sentence the magistrates
OL,17,Fcould impose may not be enough and he
OL,18,Fwould have to be sentenced instead by
OL,19,Fa judge at a crown court.
