OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FBaros has no previous convictions, a
OL,7,Fclean driving licence and had shown
OL,8,Fremorse, the court heard.
OL,10,FEarlier Andrew Hey, prosecuting, told
OL,11,Fthe court Baros drove his bus to the
OL,12,Fstation on his normal route but due to
OL,13,Fanother bus in a bay had to stop at an
OL,14,Fangle.
OL,16,FHe left his vehicle in "drive" mode
OL,17,Fwhile he tried to deploy the ramp to
OL,18,Fallow a disabled passenger off his
OL,19,Fvehicle.
