OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FBut the ramp was too high and so he
OL,7,Fgot back in his cab and when he took
OL,8,Fthe handbrake off which lowers the bus
OL,9,Fautomatically, the vehicle "lurched
OL,10,Fforward", Mr Hey said.
OL,12,FBaros tried to apply the brake but
OL,13,Finstead pressed the accelerator,
OL,14,Fcausing the bus to collide with the
OL,15,Fwomen and the bus shelter.
OL,17,FMr Hey said a collision incident
OL,18,Freport by Greater Manchester Police
OL,19,Fsaid the rules are a bus should not be
OL,20,Fparked in drive but always in neutral
OL,21,Fbefore a driver leaves his seat.
