OL,3,CDriver admits causing death of two
OL,4,Cwomen after crashing into bus shelter
OL,6,FIf he had left the bus in neutral and
OL,7,Fnot hit the accelerator the collision
OL,8,Fcould have been avoided, the report
OL,9,Fconcluded.
OL,11,FMajid Awan, mitigating, said: "Mr
OL,12,FBaros is in no way excusing what
OL,13,Fhappened and is extremely remorseful
OL,14,Fto the family of the victims.
OL,16,F"It is no more than an unfortunate
OL,17,Flapse of concentration. Tragically two
OL,18,Fmembers of the public did lose their
OL,19,Flives."
